00:40:27,220 --> 00:40:28,340
What's with her?

542
00:41:13,470 --> 00:41:14,470
Mr. Noh.

543
00:41:18,650 --> 00:41:21,230
Are you all right from the shock earlier?

544
00:41:23,780 --> 00:41:24,610
Well…

545
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:31,450
